---
// About section — bio and skills
---

<div class="mb-16">
  <h2 class="font-display text-3xl text-accent mb-8">// about</h2>
  <p class="text-text-primary leading-relaxed mb-4">
    I'm a developer who builds tools that solve real problems.
    mitools is my workshop — a collection of projects focused on
    productivity, developer experience, and making useful things.
  </p>
  <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-6">
    {['TypeScript', 'React', 'Node.js', 'Astro', 'PostgreSQL', 'Tailwind CSS'].map((skill) => (
      <span class="text-xs font-mono text-accent border border-accent/30 px-3 py-1 rounded">
        {skill}
      </span>
    ))}
  </div>
</div>
